<script>
    (adsbygoogle = window.adsbygoogle || []).push({});
</script></p>

<h2>Special Thanks</h2>

<p><strong><a href="http://qiita.com/takabosoft/items/162b6d90e00b79a7e328">Objective-C - iOS8でUIAlertViewからUIAlertControllerへ置き換えるのは大変だ</a></strong></p>
]]></content>
